<p>plainly tonight. It is rumoured that we will be going to firing line in a few day, but I think it will be another month yet 1.4.16.</p>
<p>Attaching phones onto all Coy billets 2.4.16.</p>
<p>Beleive the Bde will be shifting on the 10th. This move is supposed to be into firing line. Tommies captured some trenches to the west of this village yesterday 3.4.16.</p>
<p>Went to Hazebrouck and had an excellent time 1.4.16</p>
